				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">We are now recruiting bards!
<br />

<br />

<br />
You must be level 70
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">We raid Monday, Wednesday, Friday and Saturday from 7pm CST – 12 (ish)
<br />
If you cannot make 75% of our raids, DO NOT APPLY.
<br />
We are a RAIDING guild. Serious players only need apply.</span>
<br />

<br />
Once you are a full member, that does not mean you can slack off on raids. You are still required to have a 75% raid attendance after your probationary period is over. You WILL be guild removed if you slack off or just disappear after probation.
<br />

<br />
If you happen to get probationary status and then leave the guild with no explanation, do not bother reapplying.
<br />

<br />
We are not a family oriented guild. If you are easily offended, we are not the guild for you.
<br />

<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">Required AA’s (minimum 301)</span>
<br />

<br />
Singing Mastery 3
<br />
Instrument Mastery 3
<br />
Fading Memories
<br />
Boastful Bellow
<br />
Swift Journey 2
<br />
Ayonae’s Tutelage 3
<br />
Extended Notes 3
<br />
Sionachie's Crescendo 3
<br />
Improved Instrument/Singing Mastery
<br />
Echo of Taelosia 3
<br />
Jam Fest 3
<br />
Mystical Attuning 5
<br />
Discordant Defiance 5
<br />
Reflexive Mastery 5
<br />
Defensive Insticts 5
<br />

<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">Recommended AA's (minimum 700)</span>
<br />

<br />
Fortified Bellowing 5
<br />
Scribble Notes
<br />
Fleet of Foot 2
<br />
Selo's Enduring Cadence 3
<br />
Internal Metronome 5
<br />
Natural Durability 3
<br />
Chaotic Potential 3
<br />
Precognition 5
<br />
Thick Skin 5
<br />
Weapon Affinity 5
<br />
Improved Harmonious Attack 5
<br />
Song of Stone 3
<br />
Cacophony 3
<br />
Hastened Blades 3
<br />
Shield of Notes 3
<br />
Veteran's Wrath 3
<br />
Sinister Strikes
<br />
Mental Clarity 3
<br />
Body and Mind Rejuvenation
<br />
Origin
<br />

<br />

<br />
Required Equipment
<br />
Shrink Item
<br />
epic 1.5, or comparable percussion/string/singing/brass worn mods
<br />
Gate potions or Origin
<br />
Must be able to reach a minimum of 300 or higher in all resists unbuffed
<br />

<br />
Recommended Equipment
<br />
Voice of the Serpent or Shadowsong Cloak
<br />
Tiny Cloak of Darkest Night
<br />
Instant click buff item usable indoors (telescope, grim aura earring, 8th coldain ring, etc)
<br />

<br />

<br />
Required Flags
<br />
Anguish Signet Quest completed
<br />
Theater of Blood access
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
If you are interested in applying, please start a new topic in this forum (be sure to include if you are lacking in any of our requirements). If you have any questions, please send a tell Cantar or Dorlus.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=480280" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://i3.photobucket.com/albums/y93/Cantar/Cantsig2.jpg" border="0" /></a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
